author: Gus_263
title: Citizen of Ga-Metru
review: Vhisola, one of the six matoran of Metru Nui sets have a Kanoka disk launcher, and of course the kanoka disk that glows in the dark. The body is completely different to the other matoran years. This, can be used as armor in all toa, like the metru. The mask and it colors are so cool, with silver and blue. I rate it 5/5.

author: I_like_Lego
title: First matoran i got that has a 2001 face
review:
Someone bought this for me,but it is great!She has nice feet,nice arms,nice mask,nice body,nice kanoka disk launcher,nice 2001 face,good set for..for..some money.

PROS:)
+ Mask
+ Blue body
+ 2001 head
+ Joints
+ Disk Launcher
+ Disk
+ Disk launcher fires disk well

CONS:(
-Vhisola can move her head left an right but not up
Overall 10/10 small matoran but a great set.
